          <h4  id="mastery" class="content-subhead">Mastery</h4>
          <i><p>These somewhat arbitrary numbers give an idea of my skill level in a technology.
            The maximum, 100%, indicates what I can do best and for which I have a solid experience.
            This does not mean that I have nothing to learn about it. On the contrary!<p>
            In the same way, when the number is rather close to 0%, it does not necessarily indicate that I am bad with the technology in question.
            This may indicate a skill that has not been mobilized for a long time and / or in a version that is now obsolete.</p>
